content:
If your Government Cloud Plus org runs on Hyperforce, leverage Enhanced Omni-Channel to route work, including cases, leads, and Messaging for In-App and Web sessions. 

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

When: Salesforce is migrating some of these orgs to Hyperforce between May 10, 2024 and August 23, 2024.

How: After your org is running on Hyperforce, enable Omni-Channel, turn on Enhanced Omni-Channel, configure the presence statuses. Agents can add the Omni-Channel sidebar or widget where they work.
title: Enhance Routing with Omni-Channel for Government Cloud Plus
